import numpy as np

def calculate_determinants(matrix):
    num_submatrices = matrix.shape[1] + 4
    determinants = []
    for i in range(num_submatrices):
        submatrix = matrix[:, i:i + 5]
        det = np.linalg.det(submatrix)
        determinants.append(det)
    return determinants
